{
  "stem": "17001.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They had made my father-- being that he was the soldier, they made my father to be the responsible for the group of people in that building, because you had to make a name list that-- how many people and so on.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So-- so we thought that maybe we will get some-- some ration ticket for-- for food and that's how they want to know it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So my father didn't want to leave anybody out, that in case they won't get their ticket.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But as it turned out, they had gone into every Jewish house after we-- we were-- we left and they collected all the food.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Like if you had jam, if you had other things, they collected it and they were bringing it into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they made a kitchen, a community kitchen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So they were volunteers who were cooking.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And when they were bringing in the potatoes, they would put it down on the ground.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Then they took one of the boy whom I had my eyes on him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He was the one who was put a whip in his hand that if anybody tried to steal the potatoes, that he should hit them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I seen that, I get so disillusioned.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, my god, how could he even hold that whip in his hand?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, whom is he going to hit, his own kind, I mean.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he is-- and he was watching the potatoes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Can you give me an idea of how large this ghetto was, approximately how many blocks or buildings?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I would say [LAUGHS] is-- is really very, very hard to say, because it was a very big territory, very big territory.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would say that from here to-- to Main Street.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
